overview: "The user wanted to enhance the visual appeal of their sleep
  questionnaire app, which they felt was too generic. I began by analyzing the
  existing design, identifying areas like the color palette, form elements, and
  overall visual interest that needed improvement. The approach involved a
  comprehensive aesthetic overhaul: I introduced a calming, sleep-themed color
  palette with deep indigos, purples, and teal accents. I then redesigned key
  components such as the main questionnaire form, progress bar, intro section,
  and report section, incorporating subtle background elements, improved
  typography, and consistent card styling. All form fields, including
  checkboxes, radio buttons, and sliders, were polished for better visual
  feedback. Finally, I ensured all questionnaire sections adopted the new,
  cohesive design, transforming the app from a basic template to a professional
  and visually engaging sleep health tool."
